title: Hydrologic Model for Rapidian River near Ruckersville, VA
author: Zahura, Faria
abstract: This is a HEC-HMS model for a watershed draining to Rapidian river near Ruckerville, VA which discharges through USGS station 01665500. The model was calibrated using storm event occurring at Piedmont Research Station which is 18 miles downstream to the USGS station.
